message: Let's make a deal, Bob. I take $70, you take $30. It's a good deal for you in the first round!
I think we can both do better. I'm offering you $40, which is still more than you would get if we go to the next round.
Bob, this is your last chance for a good deal! I'll take $65, leaving you with $35.  It will be worth even less if you wait!
